question: Total revenue by customer (quantity*unit_price), top 5
sql: SELECT c.customer_id, c.name, SUM(oi.quantity * oi.unit_price) AS total_revenue FROM customers AS c JOIN orders AS o ON c.customer_id = o.customer_id JOIN order_items AS oi ON o.order_id = oi.order_id GROUP BY c.customer_id, c.name ORDER BY total_revenue DESC LIMIT 5
